sourcesContent: export default { name: 'Home', data(){ return { clima: [] } }, components: { Weather }, methods: { getWeather(){ const lat = '-35.5404833067820' ; const lon = '-58.049692027809016'; const part = 'hourly,daily'; const key = `e7ea28eea6e66941216ebf0b7faa1321`; axios.get(`https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/onecall?lat=${lat}&lon=${lon}&exclude=${part}&appid=${key}`).then( res => { console.log(res.data); if(res.status==200){ this.clima = res.data } else { console.log("nads"); } } ); } }, mounted(){ this.getWeather() } }
